replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"其實有咩資料係政府無<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6691e7d3c58299553ec749fea925dbd3cb492","tid":2173564,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"檢測間野同政府冇關既話送乜撚"},{"pid":"59c1fd3fd3a21d5cd4fc82e5d4e347b60337885e","tid":2173564,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:21:20.000Z","msg":"搵篤狗屎比佢驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231c39a7e3da641d4166a036ad3c6c302d8e61d7","tid":2173564,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">自願</span></strong><br />\n無「<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">強制</span></strong>」兩隻字<br />\n無事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8deb7273e34d45adc739898ccd8a8859840c7de1","tid":2173564,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"01b6691e7d3c58299553ec749fea925dbd3cb492","tid":2173564,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"檢測間野同政府冇關既話送乜撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"香港政府現已選用Prenetics為一共200,000食肆員工進行新型冠狀病毒檢測的計劃，以幫助控制疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地生物科技公司Prenetics宣布，近日獲得<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">中國平安集團</span></strong>旗下的平安創新投資基金（Ping An Ventures）的一千萬美元A輪融資，約7700萬港元。"},{"pid":"394b9af6235afd8b5ec8df931b33e5da1c43b757","tid":2173564,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f666910111f12c23bc6590cad62648cddba4a992","tid":2173564,"uid":182610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4c10a8a2cba06282a573531d5843aaa98100a9f","tid":2173564,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"百佳超巿呼籲員工參與政府的較高風險群組自願檢測計劃，有員工卻踢爆計劃非自願性質，員工不得拒絕。網上近日流傳一份由超級市場百佳發出的通告，指公司將會參與食環署提供的「2019冠狀病毒病檢測服務」，署方會委託Prenetics Limited為員工提供免費檢測；通告雖指檢測屬「自願性質」，惟有員工向《蘋果》反映，分店經理不理會員工反對，堅持強制店舖職員參與。<br />\n<br />\n該百佳員工表示，分店經理要求職員在本週六（29日）前，按照Prenetics的檢測指引卡提交樣本，百佳會安排檢測人員收回樣本。雖然通告僅稱「衷心呼籲各同事積極參與」，但該員工透露其所處分店的同事，因不希望向政府委託的機構提供樣本，曾向經理反映不希望參與，惟經理指是次檢測屬強制性質，員工不得拒絕。而在社交平台Facebook同樣有相關帖文，直指經理強制要求百佳員工參與檢測。<br />\n<br />\n該通告指，公司將會安排Prenetics在本月21至25日，在各分行分發「測試套裝」，員工須按套裝內指引採集深喉唾液樣本，再在指定日期內交還。如有檢測結果呈陽性，該員工將收到通知，如陰性則不會另外通知。<br />\n<br />\n百佳公關部回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，支持政府為較高風險群組安排自願性質的2019冠狀病毒病檢測服務，並安排前線員工參與自願檢測計劃；惟未有回應有否強制員工參與，及有否為參與人數定下目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=b1ba1f09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE%2F&h=4f0cf2b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"其實有咩資料係政府無<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9234bd06fc720def51a7d144a366eb242618a13c","tid":2173564,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"上個post撐百佳話自願有得揀班打手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211477c918efdaa7cd620453c3e25bb7c2d8d5d4","tid":2173564,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"394